```sql
-- Average transaction value (ATV) by ACI for Belles_cookbook_store's SwiftCharge transactions in Jan–Feb 2023
WITH
cte_filtered_payments AS (
  SELECT
    p.aci AS aci,
    p.eur_amount AS eur_amount
  FROM uploads.main.payments AS p
  WHERE p.merchant = ('Belles_cookbook_store')
    AND p.card_scheme = ('SwiftCharge')
    AND p.year = 2023
    -- Jan 1 (day 1) through Feb 28 (day 59) in non-leap year 2023
    AND p.day_of_year BETWEEN 1 AND 59
    AND p.eur_amount IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT
  aci,
  COUNT(*) AS transaction_count,
  ROUND(SUM(eur_amount), 2) AS total_eur_amount_EUR,
  ROUND(AVG(eur_amount), 2) AS avg_eur_amount_EUR
FROM cte_filtered_payments
GROUP BY
  aci
ORDER BY
  COALESCE(ROUND(AVG(eur_amount), 2), 0) ASC,
  aci ASC
```
